# TuffLogoStroke

`TxTuffLogoStroke` renders the current Tuff logo as an animated SVG. Use it for brand moments, empty-state accents, or onboarding surfaces where a static logo feels too quiet.

## Animation Modes

`once` plays the draw-in sequence on mount. `breathe` and `loop` keep a subtle pulse after the draw-in sequence. `hover` waits until the user hovers the SVG.

